        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3757267360" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13897237172028608335">I recently saw a psychic medium who suggested I invite Buddha into my spiritual practice to help sort out some of the drama in my life. (Me? Dramatic? Never! Haha.) <br/><br/>I knew nothing about the dude, so I read this book to learn more about Buddhism. I must say, altho not everything tickled my fancy, I did learn some really insightful meditation tips. And now I have a joyful Buddha statue who lives among my house plants.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


